About Us



What we doWho we serveWhat we deliverWho we employWhat we promiseWhat we doThrough a unique combination of information, analytics and expertise, IHS Markit enables smarter, better decision making in everything from day-to-day operations to long-term investments.Who we serveBusiness and governments worldwide use our unrivaled depth of industry and market information, expertise and analytical capability to make educated and informed decisions.What we deliverStrategic Planning + Operations + EngineeringOur core workflows encompasses every critical domain of business expertise.These cross-functional solutions integrate research, analysis and information into an end-to-end problem-solving platform that enables strategic planners, engineers and operational leaders to make critical business decisions.Who we employOur global team includes subject matter experts and industry specialists with broad, comprehensive experience. From the shop floor to the C-suite, clients at every level can benefit from our expertise.What we promiseFrom ground-level tactics to high-level strategy, our thinking scales across virtually any domain to help leading organizations seize the best opportunities in their industries.




