IHS Country Risk







                Integrate risk into effective decisions.
            
IHS Economics & Country Risk provides end-to-end coverage of political, violent, sovereign, banking and investment risk worldwide. Access over 50 full time analysts, dynamic forecasts and unique workflow tools—plus get integrated risk/opportunity coverage for faster collaboration across your organization. Advanced risk alerts, visualization, and analytics help you monitor local risks and calculate global exposure on an ongoing basis. Ratings for short- and medium-term sovereign risk, 54 different types of investment risk, and emerging market banking risk leverage the combined power of 200 economic and country risk analysts. Subscribe today to:
Identify, evaluate and mitigate emerging risksUnderstand local dynamics and developmentsVisualize and quantify risk exposureTailor risk ratings to your business model and industry 




Learn how IHS can help you manage country risk                
